   "source": [
    "### Lexicon Comparison\n",
    "We use **TextBlob** (Polarity & Subjectivity) and **VADER** (Compound Score).\n",
    "- **Polarity**: [-1, 1] (Negative to Positive)\n",
    "- **Subjectivity**: [0, 1] (Fact to Opinion)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 44,
   "id": "c09",
   "metadata": {
    "colab": {
     "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
    },
    "id": "c09",
